def __makeplot():

    Nrow, Ncol = 1, 3

    font = 12

    fig, ax = plt.subplots(Nrow, Ncol, figsize=(15, 5), sharex=True)

    plt.subplots_adjust(hspace=0.1)

    nbins = 20
    rmax = 1440

    ax[0].hist(durationU, bins=nbins, range=(0, rmax), log=True, rwidth=0.8, zorder=2)
